title: Women Around the World: Listener Mail January 2022 Edition
itunes:title: Women Around the World: Listener Mail January 2022 Edition
description:
We dig into the listener mail inbox to read some amazing messages about the politics in Chile and women to look out for in aviation and freediving. Keep those messages coming!
